headline: JPMorgan Says Correction Will Be “Healthy” – 5 Safe High-Yield Dividend Stocks
summary: Jamie Dimon is one of the highest-profile bankers in the world. Like Warren Buffett, David Solomon, or other Wall Street titans, when he speaks, people listen. Recently, the JPMorgan CEO called the three-year bull market run unmistakable, while warning that asset prices are currently high and credit spreads are unusually tight —a rough combination that ...
